<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation lays down the ways in which the administrative authorities in the Member States responsible for the application of laws on value added tax shall cooperate with each other and with the Commission to ensure compliance with those laws. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega n&auml;hakse ette tingimused, mille kohaselt liikmesriikides tulumaksuseaduste rakendamise eest vastutavad haldusasutused teevad omavahel ja komisjoniga koost&ouml;&ouml;d, et tagada k&otilde;nealuste seaduste j&auml;rgimine. </eesti>
<inglise> To that end it lays down procedures for the exchange of value added tax information on intra-Community transactions by electronic means and any subsequent exchange of information between Member States' competent authorities. </inglise>
<eesti> Sel eesm&auml;rgil kehtestatakse liikmesriikide p&auml;devate asutuste vahel elektroonilisel teel k&auml;ibemaksualase teabe vahetamiseks sooritatavate &uuml;hendusesiseste tehingute kord ja muu j&auml;rgneva teabevahetuse kord nende vahel. </eesti>
