<inglise> - 'value added tax identification number' shall mean the number provided for in with Article 22 (1) (c), (d) and (e) of Directive 77/388/EEC, </inglise>
<eesti> - k&auml;ibemaksukohustuslase registrinumber - direktiivi 77/388/EM&Uuml; artikli 22 l&otilde;ike 1 punktides c, d ja e etten&auml;htud number; </eesti>
<inglise> - 'intra-Community transactions' shall mean the intra-Community supply of goods and the intra-Community supply of services as defined in this paragraph, </inglise>
<eesti> - &uuml;hendusesisesed tehingud - selles l&otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;ratletud &uuml;hendusesisesed kaubatarned ja &uuml;hendusesisene teenuste osutamine, </eesti>
