<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The obligation to give assistance provided for in this Regulation shall not cover the provision of information or documents obtained by the administrative authorities referred to in Article 1 at the request of a judicial authority. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud abistamiskohustus ei k&auml;sitle artiklis 1 nimetatud p&auml;devate asutuste poolt sellise teabe v&otilde;i dokumentide esitamist, mis on saadud kohtu n&otilde;udmisel. </eesti>
